      • contentReferences

        public java.util.Collection<java.lang.String> contentReferences()
        Retrieve content references in the order defined by SMIL document.

        Content is referenced by the src attribute of par child elements. If the reference is prefixed by cid; the reference referred to is the content identifier, otherwise it is the content location.

        Returns:
        collection of ordered content identifiers. Never null.
